'''Warcloaks''' were special garments given to those on [[Shiva IV]] who had proven themselves to be honorable warriors. A warcloak which had been intended for [[Aron Peacebringer]]'s [[Aron Peacebringer's daughter|daughter]] was given by [[Alisande]] to [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]]. Alisande claimed Leia was her [[daughter in spirit]].

